snippet.title: My Indie Game Is Having An Identity Crysis - Grid:Locked Devlog #0
snippet.description:
Grid:Locked is a game about building cities. And also about some other stuff. 
Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1842280/GridLocked/

This is sort of an introduction devlog, still trying to figure out the style I'm going for.

Made in Unity 2020

➤ Twitter: https://twitter.com/eNorby
➤ Twitch: https://twitch.tv/eNorby
➤ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/eNorby1
➤ Website: https://norbert.gg

Music used:

Song: Victor Cooper - Windwalker (No Copyright Music)
Music provided by Tunetank.
Free Download:  https://bit.ly/3aUXXG6
Video Link: https://youtu.be/vNsbeLrw5Ig

Song: Float - Geographer (Youtube Audio Library)
Song: Meet & Fun! - Ofshane (Youtube Audio Library)

Shoutouts for inspiring me:
Dani: https://www.youtube.com/c/DaniDev
Randy: https://www.youtube.com/c/RandallThomas
